a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c1012%2c20221031%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉簡,1012,20221031,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"1012","JDATE":"20221031","JTITLE":"傷害"}